{
  "texts": [
    "Hence, we developed this dataset specifically to fill this gap.",
    "MetoQA is a novel dataset comprising 1100 multiple-choice questions based on the linguistic phenomenon called metonymy.",
    "Metonymy is a figure of speech in which one word or phrase is substituted with another word or phrase with which it is closely associated or related.",
    "Unlike a metaphor, where one thing is said to be another (e.g., \"Life is a journey\"), in metonymy, the substitution is based on a real, often contiguously related, connection between the two terms (e.g., \"These are my hired guns\").",
    "In this section, we describe each task and the associated dataset."
  ]
}